prompt_text: Describe the moment in your life that you cherish the most.
content_text: The moment I trust, I trust the most in my life is when I got the job opportunity. So when I got the call from the HR, I was very happy and amazed. I told my family about it and they were also very happy. My brother. Raised me and my whole family, said very proud. My mother made a special dish for me and gave me a gift. I was very happy and surprised at the same time because I wasn't expecting it. But yes, I got the job opportunity and I am very grateful for that.
